name: Trapped
review:
A movie with good intensity but not intense enough to amaze. Nevertheless, a good script and marvelous acting by Rajkummar Rao. With few dialogues, it was the director's effort that picked the movie well and kept the consistency going.

Storyline Rating: 3

Acting Rating: 4
Rajkummar Rao: 4

Direction Rating: 3

Music Rating: 2

Cinematography: 3

Editing: 2
